de.mbrero.see.console.commands

Class ParsegoldCommand

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.mbrero.see.console.commands.ParsegoldCommand
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICommand

    public class ParsegoldCommand
extends java.lang.Object
implements ICommand
    Triggers the parsing of a gold standard GoldStandardType so it can be used for the extractor evaluation as reference resource.
    The folder containing the texts should be named after the ontology/ontologies used.
    Author:
    massi.brero@gmail.com
    See Also:
    Example:
    parsegold -type craft -input {path to goldstandard}/ncbi -output {path to chosen result folder}/qrel
